00:34:52,030 --> 00:34:54,090
he created a world within a painting.

583
00:34:54,170 --> 00:34:55,510
Every blade of grass and every tree there,

584
00:34:55,510 --> 00:34:56,550
every object and every person,

585
00:34:56,550 --> 00:34:57,360
all moved according to

586
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:58,760
his thoughts and desires

