00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,260
and they couldn't escape.

588
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:01,880
Then, how were you able to escape?

589
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:03,880
T-That's really incredible.

590
00:35:05,070 --> 00:35:05,840
Yes,

591
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:08,060
it did take quite some effort.

592
00:35:08,890 --> 00:35:10,030
We faced several dangers

593
