603
00:35:28,110 --> 00:35:29,970
That demon was afraid of the moon.

604
00:35:30,300 --> 00:35:31,100
As soon as he saw

605
00:35:31,100 --> 00:35:32,430
Xuanye's precious bugs,

606
00:35:32,430 --> 00:35:33,890
he vanished into thin air.

607
