Once he died,

608
00:35:34,840 --> 00:35:36,670
the painted world also collapsed.

609
00:35:36,670 --> 00:35:37,930
We, the living humans,

610
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,150
regained our senses,

611
00:35:39,150 --> 00:35:40,560
