612
00:35:40,560 --> 00:35:41,710
The leaders of the Sky Cavern

613
00:35:41,710 --> 00:35:42,590
also came forward

614
00:35:42,590 --> 00:35:45,250
and sent the trapped people back home one by one.

615
00:35:46,110 --> 00:35:47,240
Commissioner Sima,

616
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:49,170
