617
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:54,480
I didn't.

618
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:56,920
That's really a pity.

619
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:58,440
Yes,

620
00:35:58,850 --> 00:35:59,880
it's indeed a pity

621
00:35:59,910 --> 00:36:01,180
to not be part of

622
