such a rare event.

623
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:03,500
Otherwise,

624
00:36:03,520 --> 00:36:04,670
I could have fought alongside Chief Constable Chu,

625
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:05,880
and battled and vanquished

626
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:07,010
the demon together.

627
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:09,180
Don't say that.

628
00:36:09,720 --> 00:36:10,320
You contributed

629
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,380
