630
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:11,800
Yes.

631
00:36:14,590 --> 00:36:15,190
Tingzhou,

632
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:16,840
where is your lady?

633
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:18,300
She's on the second floor.

634
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:19,780
Xuanye's room?

635
00:36:22,550 --> 00:36:24,010
Why isn't she coming down?

636
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:25,070
I'll go find her.

637
00:36:25,070 --> 00:36:25,600
Sit down.

638
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,190
Tell Chief Constable Wen properly

639
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:31,250
