644
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:37,880
Say more.

645
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:38,510
Say more.

646
00:36:40,510 --> 00:36:42,630
Commissioner Sima was looking for us outside,

647
00:36:42,630 --> 00:36:43,400
and by chance,

648
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:44,530
she found that study

649
00:36:44,590 --> 00:36:45,710
and somehow,

650
00:36:46,230 --> 00:36:47,670
she killed that demon.

651
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:50,540
That's all?

652
00:36:53,170 --> 00:36:54,370
I was in the painting.

