My father left me this

687
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:11,000
protective magic tool.

688
00:38:11,230 --> 00:38:11,960
I wanted it

689
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,600
to stay by my side

690
00:38:13,630 --> 00:38:14,480
as a token.

691
00:38:15,190 --> 00:38:16,150
But I didn't expect

692
00:38:16,150 --> 00:38:17,280
that it took the Mirage's hit

