695
00:38:20,750 --> 00:38:21,440
What a pity.

696
00:38:26,070 --> 00:38:27,510
Why are you all at my house instead of

697
00:38:27,510 --> 00:38:28,900
working in the government office?

698
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:29,760
Youhuang was telling me

699
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:31,480
about your experience in the Underground City.

700
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:32,440
Xuanye, seriously.

701
00:38:32,440 --> 00:38:33,230
Why didn't you bring me

