704
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,070
This afternoon,

705
00:38:38,070 --> 00:38:39,840
I've arranged a banquet at Yanlai Restaurant.

706
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:41,150
I hope you all can attend.

707
00:38:41,150 --> 00:38:42,480
You're leaving so soon?

708
00:38:42,630 --> 00:38:43,590
How is it soon?

709
00:38:44,230 --> 00:38:45,150
It's been half a month

710
00:38:45,150 --> 00:38:45,880
already.

