00:38:46,290 --> 00:38:47,750
If she doesn't leave soon,

712
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:49,800
she'll have to stay for the New Year.

713
00:38:52,510 --> 00:38:53,990
You seem quite resentful.

714
00:38:54,510 --> 00:38:55,220
What's wrong?

715
00:38:55,220 --> 00:38:57,280
You don't want me to stay here, do you?

716
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:58,330
I wouldn't dare.

717
00:38:59,240 --> 00:39:00,110
The case of Lord Xin'an

718
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:01,390
has been solved.

719
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:02,710
Tell me,

720
00:39:03,130 --> 00:39:03,760
do you want to

721
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,070
return to Shendu with me

722
00:39:05,070 --> 00:39:06,000
to claim credit?

723
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:08,380
Thank you, Commissioner,

724
00:39:08,770 --> 00:39:10,900
but I'm just a humble Chief Constable.

725
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:12,360
Solving this case

726
00:39:12,560 --> 00:39:14,550
was all thanks to your brilliant deductions

727
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:15,440
