730
00:39:18,190 --> 00:39:19,320
I don't need to go.

731
00:39:21,710 --> 00:39:22,240
Alright.

732
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:24,640
I'll head back to the office first then.

733
00:39:25,070 --> 00:39:26,400
See you this afternoon.

734
00:39:32,110 --> 00:39:33,510
I'll go back first.

735
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:45,000
My Lady,

736
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:46,220
