00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:01,850
likes Chief Constable Chu?

742
00:40:03,590 --> 00:40:05,120
How did you figure that out?

743
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:06,610
It's quite obvious.

744
00:40:07,190 --> 00:40:08,710
The way she looks at him is like how you look at

745
00:40:08,710 --> 00:40:09,570
Physician Jiu.

746
00:40:11,690 --> 00:40:12,330
Is that so?

747
00:40:15,170 --> 00:40:15,730
My Lady,

748
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:17,480
you've all been back

749
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:18,880
