826
00:43:13,150 --> 00:43:15,210
Commissioner Sima, you're too kind.

827
00:43:16,030 --> 00:43:17,550
Youhuang is my good friend.

828
00:43:17,550 --> 00:43:19,670
Physician Jiu, you can just call me Lingying.

829
00:43:19,670 --> 00:43:20,070
Right.

830
00:43:21,070 --> 00:43:22,130
Just good friends.

